title: Frontiers in Chemical Engineering - Research Needs and Opportuni
description:
Frontiers in Chemical Engineering - Research Needs and Opportunities (National Academy, 1988).pdf

ISBN 0309038367

Frontiers in Chemical Engineering explores the opportunities available and gives a blueprint for turning a multitude of promising visions into realities. It also examines the likely changes in how chemical engineers will be educated and take their place in the profession, and presents new research opportunities
